|Z_1 + Z_2 |^2 = (Z_1 + Z_2)\overline{(Z_1 + Z_2)}
| Z_1 + Z_2 |^2 = |Z_1|^2 + |Z_2|^2
(Z_1 \overline{Z_2})
\leq (|Z_1| + |Z_2|)^2
|z_1| = |(z_1 - z_2) + (z_2)|
z_1=r_1(\cos A+i\sin A)
z_2=r_2(\cos B+i\sin B)
|z_1|=r_1
|z_2|=r_2
|z_1-z_2|
=\sqrt{(r_1\cos A-r_2\cos B)^2+(r_1\sin A-r_2\sin B)^2}
=\sqrt{r_1^2+r_2^2-2r_1r_2\cos(A-B)}
≥\sqrt{r_1^2+r_2^2-2r_1r_2}
\cos(A-B)≤1
=r_1-r_2
|z_1-z_2|≥|z_1|-|z_2|
\cos(A-B)=1
A=B
